{
  "video_id": "2_0aEezKvBE",
  "title": "Francis Collins: We need better drugs -- now",
  "es": 1,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 0.0,
      "end_time": 16053.0,
      "text": "Translator: Joseph Geni Reviewer: Morton Bast"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 16053.0,
      "end_time": 18229.0,
      "text": "So let me ask for a show of hands."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 18229.0,
      "end_time": 22421.0,
      "text": "How many people here are over the age of 48?"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 22421.0,
      "end_time": 25302.0,
      "text": "Well, there do seem to be a few."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 25302.0,
      "end_time": 27477.0,
      "text": "Well, congratulations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 27477.0,
      "end_time": 31347.0,
      "text": "because if you look at this particular slide of U.S. life expectancy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 31347.0,
      "end_time": 34445.0,
      "text": "you are now in excess of the average life span"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 34445.0,
      "end_time": 37232.0,
      "text": "of somebody who was born in 1900."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 37232.0,
      "end_time": 40766.0,
      "text": "But look what happened in the course of that century."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 40766.0,
      "end_time": 42428.0,
      "text": "If you follow that curve,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 42428.0,
      "end_time": 45042.0,
      "text": "you'll see that it starts way down there."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 45042.0,
      "end_time": 47511.0,
      "text": "There's that dip there for the 1918 flu."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 47511.0,
      "end_time": 49933.0,
      "text": "And here we are at 2010,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 49933.0,
      "end_time": 52989.0,
      "text": "average life expectancy of a child born today, age 79,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 52989.0,
      "end_time": 54885.0,
      "text": "and we are not done yet."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 54885.0,
      "end_time": 56220.0,
      "text": "Now, that's the good news."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 56220.0,
      "end_time": 58061.0,
      "text": "But there's still a lot of work to do."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 58061.0,
      "end_time": 59695.0,
      "text": "So, for instance, if you ask,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 59695.0,
      "end_time": 62421.0,
      "text": "how many diseases do we now know"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 62421.0,
      "end_time": 64480.0,
      "text": "the exact molecular basis?"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 64480.00000000001,
      "end_time": 68038.0,
      "text": "Turns out it's about 4,000, which is pretty amazing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 68038.0,
      "end_time": 70274.0,
      "text": "because most of those molecular discoveries"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 70274.0,
      "end_time": 72939.0,
      "text": "have just happened in the last little while."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 72939.0,
      "end_time": 76235.0,
      "text": "It's exciting to see that in terms of what we've learned,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 76235.0,
      "end_time": 78342.0,
      "text": "but how many of those 4,000 diseases"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 78342.0,
      "end_time": 80690.0,
      "text": "now have treatments available?"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 80690.0,
      "end_time": 82578.0,
      "text": "Only about 250."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 82578.0,
      "end_time": 85336.0,
      "text": "So we have this huge challenge, this huge gap."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 85336.0,
      "end_time": 87916.0,
      "text": "You would think this wouldn't be too hard,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 87916.0,
      "end_time": 89442.0,
      "text": "that we would simply have the ability"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 89442.0,
      "end_time": 92468.0,
      "text": "to take this fundamental information that we're learning"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 92468.0,
      "end_time": 95613.0,
      "text": "about how it is that basic biology teaches us"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 95613.0,
      "end_time": 97515.0,
      "text": "about the causes of disease"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 97515.0,
      "end_time": 100541.0,
      "text": "and build a bridge across this yawning gap"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 100541.0,
      "end_time": 102921.0,
      "text": "between what we've learned about basic science"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 102921.0,
      "end_time": 104416.0,
      "text": "and its application,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 104416.0,
      "end_time": 107673.0,
      "text": "a bridge that would look maybe something like this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 107673.0,
      "end_time": 111285.0,
      "text": "where you'd have to put together a nice shiny way"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 111285.0,
      "end_time": 114253.0,
      "text": "to get from one side to the other."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 114253.0,
      "end_time": 116853.0,
      "text": "Well, wouldn't it be nice if it was that easy?"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 116853.0,
      "end_time": 118998.0,
      "text": "Unfortunately, it's not."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 118998.0,
      "end_time": 121589.0,
      "text": "In reality, trying to go from fundamental knowledge"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 121589.0,
      "end_time": 124253.0,
      "text": "to its application is more like this."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 124253.0,
      "end_time": 126168.0,
      "text": "There are no shiny bridges."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 126168.0,
      "end_time": 127820.0,
      "text": "You sort of place your bets."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 127820.0,
      "end_time": 129781.0,
      "text": "Maybe you've got a swimmer and a rowboat"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 129781.0,
      "end_time": 131305.0,
      "text": "and a sailboat and a tugboat"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 131305.0,
      "end_time": 133033.0,
      "text": "and you set them off on their way,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 133033.0,
      "end_time": 135697.0,
      "text": "and the rains come and the lightning flashes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 135697.0,
      "end_time": 137211.0,
      "text": "and oh my gosh, there are sharks in the water"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 137211.0,
      "end_time": 139232.0,
      "text": "and the swimmer gets into trouble,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 139232.0,
      "end_time": 140816.0,
      "text": "and, uh oh, the swimmer drowned"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 140816.0,
      "end_time": 144028.0,
      "text": "and the sailboat capsized,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 144028.0,
      "end_time": 145729.0,
      "text": "and that tugboat, well, it hit the rocks,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 145729.0,
      "end_time": 148369.0,
      "text": "and maybe if you're lucky, somebody gets across."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 148369.0,
      "end_time": 150358.0,
      "text": "Well, what does this really look like?"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 150358.0,
      "end_time": 152412.0,
      "text": "Well, what is it to make a therapeutic, anyway?"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 152412.0,
      "end_time": 155413.0,
      "text": "What's a drug? A drug is made up"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 155413.0,
      "end_time": 157738.0,
      "text": "of a small molecule of hydrogen, carbon,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 157738.0,
      "end_time": 159989.0,
      "text": "oxygen, nitrogen, and a few other atoms"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 159989.0,
      "end_time": 162212.0,
      "text": "all cobbled together in a shape,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 162212.0,
      "end_time": 164589.0,
      "text": "and it's those shapes that determine whether, in fact,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 164589.0,
      "end_time": 167902.0,
      "text": "that particular drug is going to hit its target."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 167902.0,
      "end_time": 170125.0,
      "text": "Is it going to land where it's supposed to?"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 170125.0,
      "end_time": 173281.0,
      "text": "So look at this picture here -- a lot of shapes dancing around for you."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 173281.0,
      "end_time": 175668.0,
      "text": "Now what you need to do, if you're trying to develop"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 175668.0,
      "end_time": 177125.0,
      "text": "a new treatment for autism"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 177125.0,
      "end_time": 179344.0,
      "text": "or Alzheimer's disease or cancer"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 179344.0,
      "end_time": 181136.0,
      "text": "is to find the right shape in that mix"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 181136.0,
      "end_time": 184053.0,
      "text": "that will ultimately provide benefit and will be safe."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 184053.0,
      "end_time": 187220.0,
      "text": "And when you look at what happens to that pipeline,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 187220.0,
      "end_time": 188721.0,
      "text": "you start out maybe with thousands,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 188721.0,
      "end_time": 190363.0,
      "text": "tens of thousands of compounds."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 190363.0,
      "end_time": 192512.0,
      "text": "You weed down through various steps"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 192512.0,
      "end_time": 193895.0,
      "text": "that cause many of these to fail."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 193895.0,
      "end_time": 197235.0,
      "text": "Ultimately, maybe you can run a clinical trial with four or five of these,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 197235.0,
      "end_time": 200277.0,
      "text": "and if all goes well, 14 years after you started,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 200277.0,
      "end_time": 202288.0,
      "text": "you will get one approval."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 202288.0,
      "end_time": 204318.0,
      "text": "And it will cost you upwards of a billion dollars"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 204318.0,
      "end_time": 206462.0,
      "text": "for that one success."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 206462.0,
      "end_time": 209766.0,
      "text": "So we have to look at this pipeline the way an engineer would,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 209766.0,
      "end_time": 210974.0,
      "text": "and say, \"How can we do better?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 210974.0,
      "end_time": 213651.0,
      "text": "And that's the main theme of what I want to say to you this morning."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 213651.0,
      "end_time": 215464.0,
      "text": "How can we make this go faster?"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 215464.0,
      "end_time": 218529.0,
      "text": "How can we make it more successful?"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 218529.0,
      "end_time": 219870.0,
      "text": "Well, let me tell you about a few examples"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 219870.0,
      "end_time": 222126.0,
      "text": "where this has actually worked."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 222126.0,
      "end_time": 225077.0,
      "text": "One that has just happened in the last few months"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 225077.0,
      "end_time": 228787.0,
      "text": "is the successful approval of a drug for cystic fibrosis."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 228787.0,
      "end_time": 230441.0,
      "text": "But it's taken a long time to get there."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 230441.0,
      "end_time": 235043.0,
      "text": "Cystic fibrosis had its molecular cause discovered in 1989"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 235043.0,
      "end_time": 237371.0,
      "text": "by my group working with another group in Toronto,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 237371.0,
      "end_time": 239506.0,
      "text": "discovering what the mutation was in a particular gene"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 239506.0,
      "end_time": 241134.0,
      "text": "on chromosome 7."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 241134.0,
      "end_time": 243172.0,
      "text": "That picture you see there?"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 243172.0,
      "end_time": 245275.0,
      "text": "Here it is. That's the same kid."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 245275.0,
      "end_time": 248619.0,
      "text": "That's Danny Bessette, 23 years later,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 248619.0,
      "end_time": 249898.0,
      "text": "because this is the year,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 249898.0,
      "end_time": 252336.0,
      "text": "and it's also the year where Danny got married,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 252336.0,
      "end_time": 255393.0,
      "text": "where we have, for the first time, the approval by the FDA"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 255393.0,
      "end_time": 259130.0,
      "text": "of a drug that precisely targets the defect in cystic fibrosis"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 259130.0,
      "end_time": 261068.0,
      "text": "based upon all this molecular understanding."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 261067.99999999997,
      "end_time": 262492.0,
      "text": "That's the good news."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 262492.0,
      "end_time": 266121.0,
      "text": "The bad news is, this drug doesn't actually treat all cases of cystic fibrosis,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 266121.0,
      "end_time": 268330.0,
      "text": "and it won't work for Danny, and we're still waiting"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 268330.0,
      "end_time": 270665.0,
      "text": "for that next generation to help him."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 270665.0,
      "end_time": 273860.0,
      "text": "But it took 23 years to get this far. That's too long."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 273860.0,
      "end_time": 275553.0,
      "text": "How do we go faster?"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 275553.0,
      "end_time": 278251.0,
      "text": "Well, one way to go faster is to take advantage of technology,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 278251.0,
      "end_time": 280915.0,
      "text": "and a very important technology that we depend on"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 280915.0,
      "end_time": 283211.0,
      "text": "for all of this is the human genome,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 283211.0,
      "end_time": 285799.0,
      "text": "the ability to be able to look at a chromosome,"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 285799.0,
      "end_time": 288469.0,
      "text": "to unzip it, to pull out all the DNA,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 288469.0,
      "end_time": 291419.0,
      "text": "and to be able to then read out the letters in that DNA code,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 291419.0,
      "end_time": 293500.0,
      "text": "the A's, C's, G's and T's"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 293500.0,
      "end_time": 296771.0,
      "text": "that are our instruction book and the instruction book for all living things,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 296771.0,
      "end_time": 298285.0,
      "text": "and the cost of doing this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 298285.0,
      "end_time": 300940.0,
      "text": "which used to be in the hundreds of millions of dollars,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 300940.0,
      "end_time": 302853.0,
      "text": "has in the course of the last 10 years"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 302853.0,
      "end_time": 305252.0,
      "text": "fallen faster than Moore's Law, down to the point"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 305252.0,
      "end_time": 309259.0,
      "text": "where it is less than 10,000 dollars today to have your genome sequenced, or mine,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 309259.0,
      "end_time": 313058.0,
      "text": "and we're headed for the $1,000 genome fairly soon."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 313058.0,
      "end_time": 314384.0,
      "text": "Well, that's exciting."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 314384.0,
      "end_time": 318194.0,
      "text": "How does that play out in terms of application to a disease?"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 318194.0,
      "end_time": 320474.0,
      "text": "I want to tell you about another disorder."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 320474.0,
      "end_time": 322786.0,
      "text": "This one is a disorder which is quite rare."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 322786.0,
      "end_time": 325554.0,
      "text": "It's called Hutchinson-Gilford progeria,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 325554.0,
      "end_time": 328859.0,
      "text": "and it is the most dramatic form of premature aging."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 328859.0,
      "end_time": 332642.0,
      "text": "Only about one in every four million kids has this disease,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 332642.0,
      "end_time": 336002.0,
      "text": "and in a simple way, what happens is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 336002.0,
      "end_time": 338703.0,
      "text": "because of a mutation in a particular gene,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 338703.0,
      "end_time": 341370.0,
      "text": "a protein is made that's toxic to the cell"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 341370.0,
      "end_time": 343667.0,
      "text": "and it causes these individuals to age"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 343667.0,
      "end_time": 346251.0,
      "text": "at about seven times the normal rate."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 346251.0,
      "end_time": 349394.0,
      "text": "Let me show you a video of what that does to the cell."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 349394.0,
      "end_time": 352529.0,
      "text": "The normal cell, if you looked at it under the microscope,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 352529.0,
      "end_time": 355418.0,
      "text": "would have a nucleus sitting in the middle of the cell,"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 355418.0,
      "end_time": 359297.0,
      "text": "which is nice and round and smooth in its boundaries"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 359297.0,
      "end_time": 361052.0,
      "text": "and it looks kind of like that."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 361052.0,
      "end_time": 362916.0,
      "text": "A progeria cell, on the other hand,"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 362916.0,
      "end_time": 366018.0,
      "text": "because of this toxic protein called progerin,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 366018.0,
      "end_time": 368302.0,
      "text": "has these lumps and bumps in it."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 368302.0,
      "end_time": 371317.0,
      "text": "So what we would like to do after discovering this"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 371317.0,
      "end_time": 373169.0,
      "text": "back in 2003"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 373169.0,
      "end_time": 376387.0,
      "text": "is to come up with a way to try to correct that."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 376387.0,
      "end_time": 379475.0,
      "text": "Well again, by knowing something about the molecular pathways,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 379475.0,
      "end_time": 381474.0,
      "text": "it was possible to pick"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 381474.0,
      "end_time": 384091.0,
      "text": "one of those many, many compounds that might have been useful"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 384091.0,
      "end_time": 385552.0,
      "text": "and try it out."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 385552.0,
      "end_time": 388127.0,
      "text": "In an experiment done in cell culture"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 388127.0,
      "end_time": 390169.0,
      "text": "and shown here in a cartoon,"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 390169.0,
      "end_time": 392863.0,
      "text": "if you take that particular compound"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 392863.0,
      "end_time": 396119.0,
      "text": "and you add it to that cell that has progeria,"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 396119.0,
      "end_time": 398340.0,
      "text": "and you watch to see what happened,"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 398340.0,
      "end_time": 401302.0,
      "text": "in just 72 hours, that cell becomes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 401302.0,
      "end_time": 403570.0,
      "text": "for all purposes that we can determine,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 403570.0,
      "end_time": 405412.0,
      "text": "almost like a normal cell."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 405412.0,
      "end_time": 409753.0,
      "text": "Well that was exciting, but would it actually work in a real human being?"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 409753.0,
      "end_time": 413138.0,
      "text": "This has led, in the space of only four years"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 413138.0,
      "end_time": 416639.0,
      "text": "from the time the gene was discovered to the start of a clinical trial,"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 416639.0,
      "end_time": 418836.0,
      "text": "to a test of that very compound."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 418836.0,
      "end_time": 420799.0,
      "text": "And the kids that you see here"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 420799.0,
      "end_time": 423361.0,
      "text": "all volunteered to be part of this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 423361.0,
      "end_time": 424822.0,
      "text": "28 of them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 424822.0,
      "end_time": 427917.0,
      "text": "and you can see as soon as the picture comes up"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 427917.0,
      "end_time": 431299.0,
      "text": "that they are in fact a remarkable group of young people"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 431299.0,
      "end_time": 432718.0,
      "text": "all afflicted by this disease,"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 432718.0,
      "end_time": 434967.0,
      "text": "all looking quite similar to each other."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 434967.0,
      "end_time": 436641.0,
      "text": "And instead of telling you more about it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 436641.0,
      "end_time": 440627.0,
      "text": "I'm going to invite one of them, Sam Berns from Boston,"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 440627.0,
      "end_time": 443060.0,
      "text": "who's here this morning, to come up on the stage"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 443060.0,
      "end_time": 445280.0,
      "text": "and tell us about his experience"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 445280.0,
      "end_time": 447190.0,
      "text": "as a child affected with progeria."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 447190.0,
      "end_time": 451248.0,
      "text": "Sam is 15 years old. His parents, Scott Berns and Leslie Gordon,"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 451248.0,
      "end_time": 453369.0,
      "text": "both physicians, are here with us this morning as well."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 453369.0,
      "end_time": 455907.0,
      "text": "Sam, please have a seat."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 455907.0,
      "end_time": 463227.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 463227.0,
      "end_time": 465405.0,
      "text": "So Sam, why don't you tell these folks"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 465405.0,
      "end_time": 468780.0,
      "text": "what it's like being affected with this condition called progeria?"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 468780.0,
      "end_time": 472588.0,
      "text": "Sam Burns: Well, progeria limits me in some ways."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 472588.0,
      "end_time": 476552.0,
      "text": "I cannot play sports or do physical activities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 476552.0,
      "end_time": 479756.0,
      "text": "but I have been able to take interest in things"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 479756.0,
      "end_time": 482735.0,
      "text": "that progeria, luckily, does not limit."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 482735.0,
      "end_time": 485292.0,
      "text": "But when there is something that I really do want to do"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 485292.0,
      "end_time": 488309.0,
      "text": "that progeria gets in the way of, like marching band"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 488309.0,
      "end_time": 491735.0,
      "text": "or umpiring, we always find a way to do it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 491735.0,
      "end_time": 495252.0,
      "text": "and that just shows that progeria isn't in control of my life."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 495252.0,
      "end_time": 496962.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 496962.0,
      "end_time": 498998.0,
      "text": "Francis Collins: So what would you like to say to researchers"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 498998.0,
      "end_time": 502095.0,
      "text": "here in the auditorium and others listening to this?"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 502095.0,
      "end_time": 504692.0,
      "text": "What would you say to them both about research on progeria"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 504692.0,
      "end_time": 506578.0,
      "text": "and maybe about other conditions as well?"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 506578.0,
      "end_time": 509724.0,
      "text": "SB: Well, research on progeria has come so far"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 509724.0,
      "end_time": 511966.0,
      "text": "in less than 15 years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 511966.0,
      "end_time": 516335.0,
      "text": "and that just shows the drive that researchers can have"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 516335.00000000006,
      "end_time": 519753.00000000006,
      "text": "to get this far, and it really means a lot"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 519753.00000000006,
      "end_time": 523004.00000000006,
      "text": "to myself and other kids with progeria,"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 523004.0,
      "end_time": 525828.0,
      "text": "and it shows that if that drive exists,"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 525828.0,
      "end_time": 528429.0,
      "text": "anybody can cure any disease,"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 528429.0,
      "end_time": 532376.0,
      "text": "and hopefully progeria can be cured in the near future,"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 532376.0,
      "end_time": 536133.0,
      "text": "and so we can eliminate those 4,000 diseases"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 536133.0,
      "end_time": 539140.0,
      "text": "that Francis was talking about."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 539140.0,
      "end_time": 542269.0,
      "text": "FC: Excellent. So Sam took the day off from school today"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 542269.0,
      "end_time": 547404.0,
      "text": "to be here, and he is â€” (Applause) --"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 547404.0,
      "end_time": 552220.0,
      "text": "He is, by the way, a straight-A+ student in the ninth grade"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 552220.0,
      "end_time": 553553.0,
      "text": "in his school in Boston."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 553553.0,
      "end_time": 555754.0,
      "text": "Please join me in thanking and welcoming Sam."
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 555754.0,
      "end_time": 559407.0,
      "text": "SB: Thank you very much. FC: Well done. Well done, buddy."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 559407.0,
      "end_time": 572216.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 572216.0,
      "end_time": 573932.0,
      "text": "So I just want to say a couple more things"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 573932.0,
      "end_time": 577064.0,
      "text": "about that particular story, and then try to generalize"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 577064.0,
      "end_time": 579560.0,
      "text": "how could we have stories of success"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 579560.0,
      "end_time": 583073.0,
      "text": "all over the place for these diseases, as Sam says,"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 583073.0,
      "end_time": 585592.0,
      "text": "these 4,000 that are waiting for answers."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 585592.0,
      "end_time": 587464.0,
      "text": "You might have noticed that the drug"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 587464.0,
      "end_time": 590233.0,
      "text": "that is now in clinical trial for progeria"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 590233.0,
      "end_time": 591997.0,
      "text": "is not a drug that was designed for that."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 591997.0,
      "end_time": 594859.0,
      "text": "It's such a rare disease, it would be hard for a company"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 594859.0,
      "end_time": 598589.0,
      "text": "to justify spending hundreds of millions of dollars to generate a drug."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 598589.0,
      "end_time": 600749.0,
      "text": "This is a drug that was developed for cancer."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 600749.0,
      "end_time": 602914.0,
      "text": "Turned out, it didn't work very well for cancer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 602914.0,
      "end_time": 605237.0,
      "text": "but it has exactly the right properties, the right shape,"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 605237.0,
      "end_time": 608129.0,
      "text": "to work for progeria, and that's what's happened."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 608129.0,
      "end_time": 611357.0,
      "text": "Wouldn't it be great if we could do that more systematically?"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 611357.0,
      "end_time": 615153.0,
      "text": "Could we, in fact, encourage all the companies that are out there"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 615153.0,
      "end_time": 616991.0,
      "text": "that have drugs in their freezers"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 616991.0,
      "end_time": 619193.0,
      "text": "that are known to be safe in humans"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 619193.0,
      "end_time": 621485.0,
      "text": "but have never actually succeeded in terms"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 621485.0,
      "end_time": 624341.0,
      "text": "of being effective for the treatments they were tried for?"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 624341.0,
      "end_time": 626725.0,
      "text": "Now we're learning about all these new molecular pathways --"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 626725.0,
      "end_time": 629804.0,
      "text": "some of those could be repositioned or repurposed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 629804.0,
      "end_time": 632203.0,
      "text": "or whatever word you want to use, for new applications,"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 632203.0,
      "end_time": 635172.0,
      "text": "basically teaching old drugs new tricks."
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 635172.0,
      "end_time": 637859.0,
      "text": "That could be a phenomenal, valuable activity."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 637859.0,
      "end_time": 640905.0,
      "text": "We have many discussions now between NIH and companies"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 640905.0,
      "end_time": 643029.0,
      "text": "about doing this that are looking very promising."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 643029.0,
      "end_time": 645643.0,
      "text": "And you could expect quite a lot to come from this."
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 645643.0,
      "end_time": 648682.0,
      "text": "There are quite a number of success stories one can point to"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 648682.0,
      "end_time": 651035.0,
      "text": "about how this has led to major advances."
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 651035.0,
      "end_time": 653242.0,
      "text": "The first drug for HIV/AIDS"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 653242.0,
      "end_time": 654971.0,
      "text": "was not developed for HIV/AIDS."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 654971.0,
      "end_time": 657489.0,
      "text": "It was developed for cancer. It was AZT."
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 657489.0,
      "end_time": 659490.0,
      "text": "It didn't work very well for cancer, but became"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 659490.0,
      "end_time": 661606.0,
      "text": "the first successful antiretroviral,"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 661606.0,
      "end_time": 664178.0,
      "text": "and you can see from the table there are others as well."
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 664178.0,
      "end_time": 667822.0,
      "text": "So how do we actually make that a more generalizable effort?"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 667822.0,
      "end_time": 670046.0,
      "text": "Well, we have to come up with a partnership"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 670046.0,
      "end_time": 672906.0,
      "text": "between academia, government, the private sector,"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 672906.0,
      "end_time": 675359.0,
      "text": "and patient organizations to make that so."
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 675359.0,
      "end_time": 677009.0,
      "text": "At NIH, we have started this new"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 677009.0,
      "end_time": 680209.0,
      "text": "National Center for Advancing Translational Sciences."
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 680209.0,
      "end_time": 683824.0,
      "text": "It just started last December, and this is one of its goals."
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 683824.0,
      "end_time": 685265.0,
      "text": "Let me tell you another thing we could do."
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 685265.0,
      "end_time": 688184.0,
      "text": "Wouldn't it be nice to be able to a test a drug"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 688184.0,
      "end_time": 690555.0,
      "text": "to see if it's effective and safe"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 690555.0,
      "end_time": 692656.0,
      "text": "without having to put patients at risk,"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 692656.0,
      "end_time": 695209.0,
      "text": "because that first time you're never quite sure?"
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 695209.0,
      "end_time": 697360.0,
      "text": "How do we know, for instance, whether drugs are safe"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 697360.0,
      "end_time": 700605.0,
      "text": "before we give them to people? We test them on animals."
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 700605.0,
      "end_time": 703247.0,
      "text": "And it's not all that reliable, and it's costly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 703247.0,
      "end_time": 704937.0,
      "text": "and it's time-consuming."
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 704937.0,
      "end_time": 707800.0,
      "text": "Suppose we could do this instead on human cells."
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 707800.0,
      "end_time": 710032.0,
      "text": "You probably know, if you've been paying attention"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 710032.0,
      "end_time": 711332.0,
      "text": "to some of the science literature"
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 711332.0,
      "end_time": 712988.0,
      "text": "that you can now take a skin cell"
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 712988.0,
      "end_time": 715869.0,
      "text": "and encourage it to become a liver cell"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 715869.0,
      "end_time": 718944.0,
      "text": "or a heart cell or a kidney cell or a brain cell for any of us."
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 718944.0,
      "end_time": 722096.0,
      "text": "So what if you used those cells as your test"
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 722096.0,
      "end_time": 725041.0,
      "text": "for whether a drug is going to work and whether it's going to be safe?"
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 725041.0,
      "end_time": 729272.0,
      "text": "Here you see a picture of a lung on a chip."
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 729272.0,
      "end_time": 732793.0,
      "text": "This is something created by the Wyss Institute in Boston,"
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 732793.0,
      "end_time": 735968.0,
      "text": "and what they have done here, if we can run the little video,"
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 735968.0,
      "end_time": 738104.0,
      "text": "is to take cells from an individual,"
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 738104.0,
      "end_time": 741213.0,
      "text": "turn them into the kinds of cells that are present in the lung,"
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 741213.0,
      "end_time": 743018.0,
      "text": "and determine what would happen"
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 743018.0,
      "end_time": 746095.0,
      "text": "if you added to this various drug compounds"
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 746095.0,
      "end_time": 748560.0,
      "text": "to see if they are toxic or safe."
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 748560.0,
      "end_time": 750831.0,
      "text": "You can see this chip even breathes."
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 750831.0,
      "end_time": 753448.0,
      "text": "It has an air channel. It has a blood channel."
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 753448.0,
      "end_time": 755151.0,
      "text": "And it has cells in between"
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 755151.0,
      "end_time": 757589.0,
      "text": "that allow you to see what happens when you add a compound."
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 757589.0,
      "end_time": 759361.0,
      "text": "Are those cells happy or not?"
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 759361.0,
      "end_time": 762392.0,
      "text": "You can do this same kind of chip technology"
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 762392.0,
      "end_time": 764601.0,
      "text": "for kidneys, for hearts, for muscles,"
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 764601.0,
      "end_time": 767065.0,
      "text": "all the places where you want to see whether a drug"
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 767065.0,
      "end_time": 769346.0,
      "text": "is going to be a problem, for the liver."
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 769346.0,
      "end_time": 772394.0,
      "text": "And ultimately, because you can do this for the individual,"
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 772394.0,
      "end_time": 774608.0,
      "text": "we could even see this moving to the point"
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 774608.0,
      "end_time": 778049.0,
      "text": "where the ability to develop and test medicines"
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 778049.0,
      "end_time": 781235.0,
      "text": "will be you on a chip, what we're trying to say here is"
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 781235.0,
      "end_time": 784736.0,
      "text": "the individualizing of the process of developing drugs"
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 784736.0,
      "end_time": 786984.0,
      "text": "and testing their safety."
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 786984.0,
      "end_time": 788636.0,
      "text": "So let me sum up."
    },
    {
      "index": 294,
      "start_time": 788636.0,
      "end_time": 790896.0,
      "text": "We are in a remarkable moment here."
    },
    {
      "index": 295,
      "start_time": 790896.0,
      "end_time": 792999.0,
      "text": "For me, at NIH now for almost 20 years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 296,
      "start_time": 792999.0,
      "end_time": 795600.0,
      "text": "there has never been a time where there was more excitement"
    },
    {
      "index": 297,
      "start_time": 795600.0,
      "end_time": 798185.0,
      "text": "about the potential that lies in front of us."
    },
    {
      "index": 298,
      "start_time": 798185.0,
      "end_time": 799977.0,
      "text": "We have made all these discoveries"
    },
    {
      "index": 299,
      "start_time": 799977.0,
      "end_time": 802342.0,
      "text": "pouring out of laboratories across the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 300,
      "start_time": 802342.0,
      "end_time": 805704.0,
      "text": "What do we need to capitalize on this? First of all, we need resources."
    },
    {
      "index": 301,
      "start_time": 805704.0,
      "end_time": 809259.0,
      "text": "This is research that's high-risk, sometimes high-cost."
    },
    {
      "index": 302,
      "start_time": 809259.0,
      "end_time": 811230.0,
      "text": "The payoff is enormous, both in terms of health"
    },
    {
      "index": 303,
      "start_time": 811230.0,
      "end_time": 814110.0,
      "text": "and in terms of economic growth. We need to support that."
    },
    {
      "index": 304,
      "start_time": 814110.0,
      "end_time": 816411.0,
      "text": "Second, we need new kinds of partnerships"
    },
    {
      "index": 305,
      "start_time": 816411.0,
      "end_time": 818632.0,
      "text": "between academia and government and the private sector"
    },
    {
      "index": 306,
      "start_time": 818632.0,
      "end_time": 821979.0,
      "text": "and patient organizations, just like the one I've been describing here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 307,
      "start_time": 821979.0,
      "end_time": 825559.0,
      "text": "in terms of the way in which we could go after repurposing new compounds."
    },
    {
      "index": 308,
      "start_time": 825559.0,
      "end_time": 828795.0,
      "text": "And third, and maybe most important, we need talent."
    },
    {
      "index": 309,
      "start_time": 828795.0,
      "end_time": 830936.0,
      "text": "We need the best and the brightest"
    },
    {
      "index": 310,
      "start_time": 830936.0,
      "end_time": 833793.0,
      "text": "from many different disciplines to come and join this effort --"
    },
    {
      "index": 311,
      "start_time": 833793.0,
      "end_time": 836239.0,
      "text": "all ages, all different groups --"
    },
    {
      "index": 312,
      "start_time": 836239.0,
      "end_time": 838326.0,
      "text": "because this is the time, folks."
    },
    {
      "index": 313,
      "start_time": 838326.0,
      "end_time": 841951.0,
      "text": "This is the 21st-century biology that you've been waiting for,"
    },
    {
      "index": 314,
      "start_time": 841951.0,
      "end_time": 844413.0,
      "text": "and we have the chance to take that"
    },
    {
      "index": 315,
      "start_time": 844413.0,
      "end_time": 846903.0,
      "text": "and turn it into something which will, in fact,"
    },
    {
      "index": 316,
      "start_time": 846903.0,
      "end_time": 849233.0,
      "text": "knock out disease. That's my goal."
    },
    {
      "index": 317,
      "start_time": 849233.0,
      "end_time": 851117.0,
      "text": "I hope that's your goal."
    },
    {
      "index": 318,
      "start_time": 851117.0,
      "end_time": 853797.0,
      "text": "I think it'll be the goal of the poets and the muppets"
    },
    {
      "index": 319,
      "start_time": 853797.0,
      "end_time": 855806.0,
      "text": "and the surfers and the bankers"
    },
    {
      "index": 320,
      "start_time": 855806.0,
      "end_time": 858084.0,
      "text": "and all the other people who join this stage"
    },
    {
      "index": 321,
      "start_time": 858084.0,
      "end_time": 859834.0,
      "text": "and think about what we're trying to do here"
    },
    {
      "index": 322,
      "start_time": 859834.0,
      "end_time": 860999.0,
      "text": "and why it matters."
    },
    {
      "index": 323,
      "start_time": 860999.0,
      "end_time": 863769.0,
      "text": "It matters for now. It matters as soon as possible."
    },
    {
      "index": 324,
      "start_time": 863769.0,
      "end_time": 866887.0,
      "text": "If you don't believe me, just ask Sam."
    },
    {
      "index": 325,
      "start_time": 866887.0,
      "end_time": 868330.0,
      "text": "Thank you all very much."
    },
    {
      "index": 326,
      "start_time": 868330.0,
      "end_time": 878330.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}